<mat-button-toggle-group name="transportType" aria-label="Transport Request" class="buttonToggleGroup"
	#group2="matButtonToggleGroup" [value]="transportType"
	(change)="onValChange('transportType', group2.value)">
	<mat-button-toggle value="flight">Flight</mat-button-toggle>
	<mat-button-toggle value="bus">Bus</mat-button-toggle>
	<mat-button-toggle value="train">Train</mat-button-toggle>
</mat-button-toggle-group>

<mat-button-toggle-group name="actionType" aria-label="Action Request" class="buttonToggleGroup"
	#group="matButtonToggleGroup" [value]="actionType" (change)="onValChange('actionType', group.value)">
	<mat-button-toggle value="new-ticket">New Ticket</mat-button-toggle>
	<mat-button-toggle value="re-schedule">Re-Schedule</mat-button-toggle>
	<mat-button-toggle value="cancellation">Cancellation</mat-button-toggle>
</mat-button-toggle-group>

<mat-form-field [floatLabel]="'never'" appearance="legacy">
	<input matInput type="text" placeholder="In which country do you need Accommodation?"
	[(ngModel)]="newTicket.info[0].countryOfAccommodation" name="countryOfAccommodation" class="capitalize">
</mat-form-field>

<mat-form-field [floatLabel]="'never'" appearance="legacy">
	<input matInput type="text" placeholder="Please enter Client address"
	[(ngModel)]="newTicket.info[0].clientAddress" name="clientAddress" class="capitalize">
</mat-form-field>

<mat-form-field [floatLabel]="'never'" appearance="legacy">
	<input matInput [matDatepicker]="checkInDate" readonly placeholder="Select Departure Date" 
	[(ngModel)]="newTicket.info[0].checkInDate" name="checkInDate" [min]="newTicket.info[0]['departureDate']"
	(click)="checkInDate.open()" data-date-format="DD/MM/YYYY">
	<mat-datepicker-toggle matSuffix [for]="checkInDate"></mat-datepicker-toggle>
	<mat-datepicker #checkInDate></mat-datepicker>
</mat-form-field>

<mat-form-field [floatLabel]="'never'" appearance="legacy">
	<input matInput [matDatepicker]="checkOutDate" readonly placeholder="Select Departure Date" 
	[(ngModel)]="newTicket.info[0].checkOutDate" name="checkOutDate" [min]="newTicket.info[0].checkInDate"
	(click)="checkOutDate.open()" data-date-format="DD/MM/YYYY">
	<mat-datepicker-toggle matSuffix [for]="checkOutDate"></mat-datepicker-toggle>
	<mat-datepicker #checkOutDate></mat-datepicker>
</mat-form-field>
